rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0001
rows.name:
It looks as if we're almost ready to
proceed with the evacuation.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0002
rows.name:
If it wasn't for all your support, we
might never have been able to pull this
off. I thank you, in the name of Iira.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0003
rows.name:
I don't know why you're thanking me.
I'm a knight now, remember?

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0004
rows.name: And you know what else?

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0006
rows.name: I'm really starting to like this place.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0007
rows.name:
You get to see so many different walks
of life here. It's a real melting pot.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0008
rows.name:
I've noticed that. So many intertwining
lives, all together in one place...

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0009
rows.name:
I have felt the same about the cities
of Superbia. There is much to like
about their urban environs.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0010
rows.name:
You're making me want to pay a visit
now!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0011
rows.name:
Then we can all go together. We'll
finish off Metsu and take Hugo back
home personally.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0012
rows.name: Oh, yes please!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0013
rows.name:
We will welcome you with open arms.
The streets will be awash with cheer!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0014
rows.name:
Uh, I'd appreciate it if we could skip
any of the formal stuff...

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0015
rows.name: ...Hey. Listen...

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0016
rows.name:
Do you think we'll...even stand
a chance? Against Metsu?

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0017
rows.name:
Haven't a clue. His power seems so far
off the charts, I couldn't even guess.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0018
rows.name: He still has his limits. And besides...

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0019
rows.name:
Adel's never been able to handle
me as effectively as he can now.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0020
rows.name:
That's right! Adel-sama's more than
prepared to take that creep down now!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0021
rows.name:
And we'll be right there to watch it
happen! Won't we Sata?

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0022
rows.name:
We've come this far...
May as well go see it through...

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0023
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Those lads...

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0024
rows.name: You're not serious?

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0025
rows.name:
Do you know how dangerous it is to be
even remotely near Metsu?

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0026
rows.name:
Just by tagging along with us, you're
putting your lives on the line!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0027
rows.name:
Oh, and I suppose we've been perfectly
safe up till now as well, have we? We
know what we're getting into, OK?!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0028
rows.name:
You don't know what you're talking
about!

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0029
rows.name:
Hikari, drop it. Come on, let's head
back to the inn.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0030
rows.name:
I want to get a good night's sleep
before the decisive battle.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0031
rows.name: Very wise.

rows.label: fev11_670_175_msg0032
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I'll really have to talk this through
with Satahiko and Milt...
